ComicInfo.Title: none; Prey; In the Beginning...; The Princess Leia Diaries; Tall Tales; Ghost
ComicInfo.Summary:
Darth Vader and Boba Fett both try to capture Han Solo in a story set sometime before The Empire Strikes Back.
Han Solo wins the Millenium Falcon from Lando Calrissian in a game of sabacc.
The life and times of Princess Leia.
Quinlan Vos and Han Solo cross paths in an adventure set between Revenge of the Sith and A New Hope.
